pageContext.claim: “In other words, Russia was against Trump in the 2016 Election - and why not, I want strong military & low oil prices. Witch Hunt! (Retweeted @foxandfriends Firm behind anti-Trump dossier also worked for Russia, Senate witness says)”
pageContext.analysis: The information on Russian efforts to sway the 2016 election was developed by the intelligence community and published in a declassified report, in which the agencies said they had "high confidence" it was correct.
